<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/4477.Complications"><img alt="Complications: A Surgeon&#39;s Notes on an Imperfect Science" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1441151524l/4477._SX98_.jpg" />
